name: Senior #21 - Gene
description:
Gene is a mysterious senior who has the superpower to emit laser beams from his eyes. Born with red hair, the color never changed even after living for centuries. He’s never seen speaking to anyone, but then again he is rarely spotted in public. He is extremely wise and enigmatic, but often misunderstood.

Rumour has it that he comes from another planet, as a hot-dog stand owner once overheard him mumbling in an otherworldly tongue.
